text: National Street (Czech title: Národní třída) is a 2019 Czech drama film starring Hynek Čermák. It is based on a book by Jaroslav Rudiš of the same name. ==Plot== The film is about man known as Vandam. He lives in prefab housing estate in Prague. He trains every night to be fits which earns him nickname reminiscent of Jean-Claude Van Damme. He likes barmaid Lucka who gets into trouble due to debts and Vandam decides to help her. ==Cast== * Hynek Čermák as Vandam * Kateřina Janečková as Lucka * Jan Cina as Psycho * Václav Neužil ml. as Milner * Jiří Langmajer * Martin Sobotka * Erika Stárková * Lubor Šplíchal * Andrej Polák * Martin Siničák * Bára Vozková * Terezie Vraspírová ==Production== Shooting started on 27 August 2018. Production concluded in July 2019.
